insight.name: Line chart
insight.derived_name: Pageview count & Interacted with file count & Custom name count
insight.hogql:
SELECT
    arrayMap(number -> plus(toStartOfDay(assumeNotNull(toDateTime('2024-07-11 00:00:00'))), toIntervalDay(number)), range(0, plus(coalesce(dateDiff('day', toStartOfDay(assumeNotNull(toDateTime('2024-07-11 00:00:00'))), toStartOfDay(assumeNotNull(toDateTime('2024-07-18 23:59:59'))))), 1))) AS date,
    arrayMap(_match_date -> arraySum(arraySlice(groupArray(count), indexOf(groupArray(day_start) AS _days_for_count, _match_date) AS _index, plus(minus(arrayLastIndex(x -> equals(x, _match_date), _days_for_count), _index), 1))), date) AS total
FROM
    (SELECT
        sum(total) AS count,
        day_start
    FROM
        (SELECT
            count() AS total,
            toStartOfDay(timestamp) AS day_start
        FROM
            events AS e SAMPLE 1
        WHERE
            and(greaterOrEquals(timestamp, toStartOfDay(assumeNotNull(toDateTime('2024-07-11 00:00:00')))), lessOrEquals(timestamp, assumeNotNull(toDateTime('2024-07-18 23:59:59'))), equals(event, '$pageview'), in(person_id, (SELECT
                        person_id
                    FROM
                        raw_cohort_people
                    WHERE
                        and(equals(cohort_id, 2), equals(version, 251)))))
        GROUP BY
            day_start)
    GROUP BY
        day_start
    ORDER BY
        day_start ASC)
ORDER BY
    arraySum(total) DESC
LIMIT 50000
UNION ALL
